100 AC\">100</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table><div>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-even\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n</div><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks collapsible uncollapsed navbox-subgroup\" style=\"border-spacing:0;width:100%;;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><span style=\"float:left;width:6em;\">&#160;</span><div class=\"\" style=\"font-size:110%;\">\nSecond century since Aegon's Conquest</div></th></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/101_AC\" title=\"101 AC\">101</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/103_AC\" title=\"103 AC\">103</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/104_AC\" title=\"104 AC\">104</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/105_AC\" title=\"105 AC\">105</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/106_AC\" title=\"106 AC\">106</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/111_AC\" title=\"111 AC\">111</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/120_AC\" title=\"120 AC\">120</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/127_AC\" title=\"127 AC\">127</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/128_AC\" title=\"128 AC\">128</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/129_AC\" title=\"129 AC\">129</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/130_AC\" title=\"130 AC\">130</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/131_AC\" title=\"131 AC\">131</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/132_AC\" title=\"132 AC\">132</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/133_AC\" title=\"133 AC\">133</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/134_AC\" title=\"134 AC\">134</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/135_AC\" title=\"135 AC\">135</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/136_AC\" title=\"136 AC\">136</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/160_AC\" title=\"160 AC\">160</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/161_AC\" title=\"161 AC\">161</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/184_AC\" title=\"184 AC\">184</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/196_AC\" title=\"196 AC\">196</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table><div>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n</div><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks collapsible uncollapsed navbox-subgroup\" style=\"border-spacing:0;width:100%;;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><span style=\"float:left;width:6em;\">&#160;</span><div class=\"\" style=\"font-size:110%;\">\nThird century since Aegon's Conquest</div></th></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/209_AC\" title=\"209 AC\">209</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/211_AC\" title=\"211 AC\">211</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/212_AC\" title=\"212 AC\">212</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/219_AC\" title=\"219 AC\">219</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/233_AC\" title=\"233 AC\">233</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/236_AC\" title=\"236 AC\">236</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/259_AC\" title=\"259 AC\">259</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/260_AC\" title=\"260 AC\">260</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/261_AC\" title=\"261 AC\">261</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/262_AC\" title=\"262 AC\">262</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/280_AC\" title=\"280 AC\">280</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/281_AC\" title=\"281 AC\">281</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/282_AC\" title=\"282 AC\">282</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">283</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/284_AC\" title=\"284 AC\">284</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/285_AC\" title=\"285 AC\">285</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/289_AC\" title=\"289 AC\">289</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/290_AC\" title=\"290 AC\">290</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/295_AC\" title=\"295 AC\">295</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/297_AC\" title=\"297 AC\">297</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/298_AC\" title=\"298 AC\">298</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/299_AC\" title=\"299 AC\">299</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/300_AC\" title=\"300 AC\">300</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table><div>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><br />\n</p><p><b>Year 283 After the Conquest</b> (<b>283 AC</b>) is a year in the <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">Westerosi calendar</a>, the 283rd after <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon I Targaryen\">Aegon</a>'s crowning in <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a> that maesters and educated people use as a reference to date the years.\n</p><p>283 AC saw the second half of <a href=\"/index.php/Robert%27s_Rebellion\" title=\"Robert&#39;s Rebellion\">Robert's Rebellion</a>, which ended with the death of Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaegar_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaegar Targaryen\">Rhaegar Targaryen</a> on the <a href=\"/index.php/Trident\" title=\"Trident\">Trident</a>, and with the deaths of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys II Targaryen\">Aerys II Targaryen</a> and Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_Targaryen_(son_of_Rhaegar)\" title=\"Aegon Targaryen (son of Rhaegar)\">Aegon Targaryen</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Sack_of_King%27s_Landing\" title=\"Sack of King&#39;s Landing\">Sack of King's Landing</a>. Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaella_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaella Targaryen\">Rhaella Targaryen</a> had fled the city with her son, Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Viserys_Targaryen\" title=\"Viserys Targaryen\">Viserys Targaryen</a>, whilst pregnant with Aerys' last child, <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a>. The Sack of King's Landing was followed by the coronation of <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_Baratheon\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Robert Baratheon\">Robert Baratheon</a> as the new king, the lifting of the <a href=\"/index.php/Siege_of_Storm%27s_End\" title=\"Siege of Storm&#39;s End\">Siege of Storm's End</a> and the death of <a href=\"/index.php/Lyanna_Stark\" title=\"Lyanna Stark\">Lyanna Stark</a> at the <a href=\"/index.php/Tower_of_Joy\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Tower of Joy\">Tower of Joy</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Events</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Births\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Births</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Deaths\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Deaths</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Events\">Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=283_AC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Bells\" title=\"Battle of the Bells\">Battle of the Bells</a> is fought between the royalist army and ther rebels. The victory belongs to the rebels, though the royalist army manages to pull back in good order.</li>\n<li>Due to the outcome of the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Bells\" title=\"Battle of the Bells\">Battle of the Bells</a>, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Connington\" title=\"Jon Connington\">Jon Connington</a> is fired from the office of <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">Hand of the King</a>. Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Qarlton_Chelsted\" title=\"Qarlton Chelsted\">Qarlton Chelsted</a> is named in his stead.</li>\n<li>Besides being fired as <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">Hand of the King</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Connington\" title=\"Jon Connington\">Jon Connington</a> is stripped of his lands and exiled by King <a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys II Targaryen\">Aerys II Targaryen</a>.</li>\n<li>Wedding of <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Tully\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Catelyn Tully\">Catelyn Tully</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Arryn\" title=\"Jon Arryn\">Jon Arryn</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Lysa_Tully\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lysa Tully\">Lysa Tully</a>, at <a href=\"/index.php/Riverrun\" title=\"Riverrun\">Riverrun</a> after the Battle of the Bells.</li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Barristan_Selmy\" title=\"Barristan Selmy\">Barristan Selmy</a> and Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Darry\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Jon Darry\">Jon Darry</a> are sent out by King <a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys II Targaryen\">Aerys II Targaryen</a> to regroup the royalist army in the Riverlands.</li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Gerold_Hightower\" title=\"Gerold Hightower\">Gerold Hightower</a> is send out by King <a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys II Targaryen\">Aerys II Targaryen</a> to find Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaegar_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaegar Targaryen\">Rhaegar Targaryen</a>.</li>\n<li>Crown Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaegar_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaegar Targaryen\">Rhaegar Targaryen</a> returns from the south and marshals an army.</li>\n<li>King <a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys II Targaryen\">Aerys II Targaryen</a> begins plotting the <a href=\"/index.php/Wildfire_plot\" title=\"Wildfire plot\">Wildfire plot</a> with his pyromancers.</li>\n<li>Upon discovering the wildfire plot, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Qarlton_Chelsted\" title=\"Qarlton Chelsted\">Qarlton Chelsted</a> resigns as <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">Hand of the King</a>. For this act, King <a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys II Targaryen\">Aerys II Targaryen</a> has him burned alive. The pyromancer <a href=\"/index.php/Rossart\" title=\"Rossart\">Rossart</a> is named <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">Hand of the King</a> in his stead.</li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Trident\" title=\"Battle of the Trident\">Battle of the Trident</a>, deciding victory for the rebels.</li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Sack_of_King%27s_Landing\" title=\"Sack of King&#39;s Landing\">Sack of King's Landing</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Robert_Baratheon\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Robert Baratheon\">Robert Baratheon</a> is crowned King.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a> lifts the siege of <a href=\"/index.php/Storm%27s_End\" title=\"Storm&#39;s End\">Storm's End</a>.</li>\n<li>Battle at <a href=\"/index.php/Tower_of_Joy\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Tower of Joy\">Tower of Joy</a>.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Births\">Births</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=283_AC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Births\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Bella\" title=\"Bella\">Bella</a>, a girl from the Riverlands, bastard daughter of <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_Baratheon\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Robert Baratheon\">Robert Baratheon</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Desmera_Redwyne\" title=\"Desmera Redwyne\">Desmera Redwyne</a>, daughter of <a href=\"/index.php/Paxter_Redwyne\" title=\"Paxter Redwyne\">Paxter Redwyne</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Mina_Tyrell\" title=\"Mina Tyrell\">Mina Tyrell</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jeyne_Westerling\" title=\"Jeyne Westerling\">Jeyne Westerling</a>, daughter of <a href=\"/index.php/Gawen_Westerling\" title=\"Gawen Westerling\">Gawen Westerling</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Sybell_Spicer\" title=\"Sybell Spicer\">Sybell Spicer</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a>, bastard son of <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a> by an unknown woman.<sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lucos_Chyttering\" title=\"Lucos Chyttering\">Lucos Chyttering</a>, son of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/House_Chyttering\" title=\"House Chyttering\">Chyttering</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Margaery_Tyrell\" title=\"Margaery Tyrell\">Margaery Tyrell</a>, daughter of <a href=\"/index.php/Mace_Tyrell\" title=\"Mace Tyrell\">Mace Tyrell</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Alerie_Hightower\" title=\"Alerie Hightower\">Alerie Hightower</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Meera_Reed\" title=\"Meera Reed\">Meera Reed</a>, daughter of <a href=\"/index.php/Howland_Reed\" title=\"Howland Reed\">Howland Reed</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Jyana\" title=\"Jyana\">Jyana</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Robb_Stark\" title=\"Robb Stark\">Robb Stark</a>, son of <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Tully\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Catelyn Tully\">Catelyn Tully</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Robert_Frey_(son_of_Raymund)\" title=\"Robert Frey (son of Raymund)\">Robert Frey</a>, son of <a href=\"/index.php/Raymund_Frey\" title=\"Raymund Frey\">Raymund Frey</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Beony_Beesbury\" title=\"Beony Beesbury\">Beony Beesbury</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Samwell_Tarly\" title=\"Samwell Tarly\">Samwell Tarly</a>, son of <a href=\"/index.php/Randyll_Tarly\" title=\"Randyll Tarly\">Randyll Tarly</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Melessa_Florent\" title=\"Melessa Florent\">Melessa Florent</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-10\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>(Roughly) <a href=\"/index.php/Del\" title=\"Del\">Del</a>, a wildling.<sup id=\"cite_ref-11\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-11\">&#91;11&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Deaths\">Deaths</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=283_AC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Deaths\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Myles_Mooton\" title=\"Myles Mooton\">Myles Mooton</a> slain by <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_Baratheon\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Robert Baratheon\">Robert Baratheon</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Bells\" title=\"Battle of the Bells\">Battle of the Bells</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Denys_Arryn\" title=\"Denys Arryn\">Denys Arryn</a> slain by <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Connington\" title=\"Jon Connington\">Jon Connington</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Bells\" title=\"Battle of the Bells\">Battle of the Bells</a>.</li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Qarlton_Chelsted\" title=\"Qarlton Chelsted\">Qarlton Chelsted</a>, burned alive after his resignation as <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">Hand of the King</a>.</li>\n<li>Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaegar_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaegar Targaryen\">Rhaegar Targaryen</a>, slain by <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_Baratheon\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Robert Baratheon\">Robert Baratheon</a> on the Trident.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_stormlands:_house_baratheon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_12-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_stormlands:_house_baratheon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-12\">&#91;12&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Lewyn_Martell\" title=\"Lewyn Martell\">Lewyn Martell</a>, slain during the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Trident\" title=\"Battle of the Trident\">Battle of the Trident</a>.</li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Jonothor_Darry\" title=\"Jonothor Darry\">Jonothor Darry</a>, slain during <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Trident\" title=\"Battle of the Trident\">Battle of the Trident</a>.</li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Rossart\" title=\"Rossart\">Rossart</a>, Hand of the King, slain by <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime Lannister</a> during the Sack of King's Landing.</li>\n<li>King <a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys II Targaryen\">Aerys II Targaryen</a>, killed by <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime Lannister</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Sack_of_King%27s_Landing\" title=\"Sack of King&#39;s Landing\">Sack of King's Landing</a>.</li>\n<li>Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_Targaryen_(son_of_Rhaegar)\" title=\"Aegon Targaryen (son of Rhaegar)\">Aegon Targaryen</a>, dashed against a wall by Gregor Clegane during the Sack of King's Landing.</li>\n<li>Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Elia_Martell\" title=\"Elia Martell\">Elia Martell</a>, raped and murdered by <a href=\"/index.php/Gregor_Clegane\" title=\"Gregor Clegane\">Gregor Clegane</a> during the Sack of King's Landing.</li>\n<li>Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaenys_Targaryen_(daughter_of_Rhaegar)\" title=\"Rhaenys Targaryen (daughter of Rhaegar)\">Rhaenys Targaryen</a>, stabbed half a hundred times by <a href=\"/index.php/Amory_Lorch\" title=\"Amory Lorch\">Amory Lorch</a> during the Sack of King's Landing.</li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Pisswater_prince\" title=\"Pisswater prince\">Pisswater prince</a>, the infant who reportedly died in place of Aegon Targaryen.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Gawen_Wylde\" title=\"Gawen Wylde\">Gawen Wylde</a>, died in the cells of <a href=\"/index.php/Storm%27s_End\" title=\"Storm&#39;s End\">Storm's End</a>.</li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Gerold_Hightower\" title=\"Gerold Hightower\">Gerold Hightower</a>, at the <a href=\"/index.php/Tower_of_Joy\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Tower of Joy\">Tower of Joy</a>.</li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Arthur_Dayne\" title=\"Arthur Dayne\">Arthur Dayne</a>, at the <a href=\"/index.php/Tower_of_Joy\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Tower of Joy\">Tower of Joy</a>.</li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Oswell_Whent\" title=\"Oswell Whent\">Oswell Whent</a>, at the <a href=\"/index.php/Tower_of_Joy\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Tower of Joy\">Tower of Joy</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lyanna_Stark\" title=\"Lyanna Stark\">Lyanna Stark</a>, in unknown circumstances.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ashara_Dayne\" title=\"Ashara Dayne\">Ashara Dayne</a>, jumped from a tower at <a href=\"/index.php/Starfall\" title=\"Starfall\">Starfall</a> into the sea.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=283_AC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap mw-references-columns\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i>See the calculation for: <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest/Calculations_Ages#Bella\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest/Calculations Ages\">Bella</a></i></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i>See the calculation for: <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest/Calculations_Ages#Desmera_Redwyne\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest/Calculations Ages\">Desmera Redwyne</a></i></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i>See the calculation for: <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest/Calculations_Ages_(Continued)#Jeyne_Westerling\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest/Calculations Ages (Continued)\">Jeyne Westerling</a></i></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i>See the calculation for: <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest/Calculations_Ages_(Continued)#Jon_Snow\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest/Calculations Ages (Continued)\">Jon Sn